errors.prescription:
1. Use optional binding: if let value = optionalValue { ... }
2. Use guard-let: guard let value = optionalValue else { return }
3. Use optional chaining: optionalValue?.member
4. Use nil-coalescing: optionalValue ?? defaultValue
5. Use force unwrap only when you are certain the value is not nil: optionalValue!

